callToAction: NSLOCTEXT("", "49C3F8014BCE6AD76028ACB5E42483E9", "Find your way to the lowlands to undercut the apothecary.")
description: NSLOCTEXT("", "69BB799F4115CDA7193579901484C855", "At the apothecary, a hooded patron offers to undercut the merchant alchemist. After the shop was robbed during the last siege, the merchant has gouged prices for faulty contraband, and needs to replenish his salves on the cheap. The sordid patron thinks he can save a pretty penny by collecting the supplies himself, since it\'s worth the same if the fish oil is collected from the fisherman he knows in the Skip. There\'s bound to be trouble along the road, but it might worth the hassle to try to fetch the same deal.")
name: SAQ_0008_DescentToTheBackwaters
